------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                |
|                            Table                               | 
------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                 |              |
|Responsibilities:                                |Collaborators |
------------------------------------------------------------------
| (1)Know table status( avaliable / unavaliable). |Admin         |  
| (2)know how many people can the table hold.     |              | 
| (3)Set table status.                            |              | 
| (4)Get table status.                            |              | 
------------------------------------------------------------------


---------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                         |
|                            Party                                        | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                          |              |
|Responsibilities:                                         |Collaborators |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
| (1)Know the number of people in the party.               |Admin         |  
| (2)Know the reply which the party send to the Admin.     |              | 
| (3)Set reply.                                            |              | 
| (4)Get reply.                                            |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------




------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                            |
|                           Admin                                            | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                             |              |
|Responsibilities:                                            |Collaborators |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| (1)Know the amount of tables.                               |Party         |  
| (2)Know the amount of parties.                              |Table         | 
| (3)Attach Admin to the parties waiting in line.             |              | 
| (4)Detach Admin from the parties which left or went to eat. |              | 
| (5)Notify party which is qualified for the empty table.     |              | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Explanation:
In my opinion, the restaurant admin knows the status of the table. And once the status is changed, admin can send message to the parties 
waiting in line. In this case, parties should be observers and admin should be the subject. And also this is not a broadcast, the message must
be sent to specific party which is qualified.
